Hotpack - Square Cake Board Silver - 50 pcs - Present your personal size treats in style with this hotpack square cake board. This sturdy circle supports your delicious creations and will sit perfectly in any window display or on any table. The innovative side tab will allow you and your patrons to carry the circle with ease.

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - Biodegradable Cling Film Food Warp 45cm x 400mtr - 6 pcs
Short Description: Hotpack - Biodegradable Cling Film Food Warp 45cm x 400mtr - 6 pcs
Description:
Hotpack - Biodegradable Cling Film Food Warp 45cm x 400mtr - 6 pcs - With the rising global demand for eco-friendly plastic products, hotpack is proud to offer bio-degradable pvc film for food wrapping material. Bio-wrap is an innovative, new concept product that uses biomass as raw materials. It is an environmentally friendly and harmless packaging material for living beings as it decomposes in nature when disposed of.

Korean biomass certificationusda biomass certification carbon footprint the oxidized biodegradable film is decomposed by microorganism, temperature, moisture, etc. In the natural state used after disposal and is virtually circulated to nature. Only using harmless raw material that is food grade and naturally obtained and no significant negative effect on the eco-system. Regular cling film is trashed and just like other plastic waste which doesn’t decompose as required and gets accumulated in nature around. It will affect the place where it is trashed whether in soil or ocean this will have an impact on our ecosystem. Hence by using this bio-degradable wrap, we can contribute to the safe being of nature.

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - Disposable Wrapped Mint Tooth Pick - 12000 pcs
Short Description: Hotpack - Disposable Wrapped Mint Tooth Pick - 12000 pcs
Description:
Hotpack - Disposable Wrapped Mint Tooth Pick - 12000 pcs - These individually wrapped mint toothpicks are a simple, yet extremely beneficial addition to your restaurant or cafe! Make a hospitable gesture, and give your guests or customers the extra comfort they want by setting these toothpicks out for use during or after their meal. Each toothpick comes individually wrapped in cellophane for sanitary dispensing, which is perfect for your high volume establishment where dozens of individuals are reaching into the dispenser a day. This gives your guests peace of mind knowing their toothpick hasn't been exposed to outside germs and debris. 

Plus, if someone accidentally drops one, it's completely covered so it can still be safely used! made of all white birch, these toothpicks are incredibly solid, smooth, and burr free, and they are less likely to splinter during use. With no added flavor or color, these plain toothpicks are sure to meet the needs of every customer. Packaged in a convenient self-dispensing box, these toothpicks can be placed out for grabs next to your hostess stand, at your concierge counter or dining room tables.

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - Wrapped Tooth Picks - 1000 pcs x 12 Packets
Short Description: Hotpack - Wrapped Tooth Picks - 1000 pcs x 12 Packets
Description:
Hotpack - Wrapped Tooth Picks - 1000 pcs x 12 Packets - These individually wrapped plain toothpicks are a simple, yet extremely beneficial addition to your restaurant or cafe! Make a hospitable gesture, and give your guests or customers the extra comfort they want by setting these toothpicks out for use during or after their meal. Each toothpick comes individually wrapped in cellophane for sanitary dispensing, which is perfect for your high volume establishment where dozens of individuals are reaching into the dispenser a day. 

This gives your guests peace of mind knowing their toothpick hasn't been exposed to outside germs and debris. Plus, if someone accidentally drops one, it's completely covered so it can still be safely used! Made of all white birch, these toothpicks are incredibly solid, smooth, and burr free, and they are less likely to splinter during use. With no added flavor or color, these plain toothpicks are sure to meet the needs of every customer. Packaged in a convenient self-dispensing box, these toothpicks can be placed out for grabs next to your hostess stand, at your concierge counter or dining room tables.

Short Description: Hotpack - Paper Boat Tray, Large - 600 pcs
Description:
Hotpack - Paper Boat Tray, Large - 600 pcs - Easily serve a wide variety of tasty finger foods, freshly made sides, and signature snacks with this paper food boat tray. Versatile in use, the tray is great for french fries, chicken tenders, mozzarella sticks, and other popular fried favorites, or with cold items such as veggies, fruit, and pasta salad. The one-piece coated paper construction ensures sturdy and reliable use, while the open top design allows users to effortlessly top off their tray with assorted sauces, dips, and condiments. Plus, an attractive hearthstone pattern adds a rustic, yet contemporary feel to any setting.

Product Specifications

Sturdy, one-piece design
Grease-resistant barrier eliminates need for liners
Hot and cold food friendly
Offers quick and easy portion control
Perfect for concession stands and picnics

Description:
Hotpack - Kraft Boat Tray, Large - 700 pcs - This kraft boat food tray is ideal for your high-traffic concession stand, drive-through window, or quick-serve restaurant. Featuring a natural kraft paper material, this food tray is both eco-friendly and easily disposable! Simply throw it away or recycle it after use and make the cleanup process easier than ever before. Featuring moisture and grease-proof coating, this food tray prevents leaking bottoms and weakening sides from moist or fried foods. Thanks to this protective barrier, you won't have to worry about grease leaking onto your countertops or your patrons' clothes!

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - Kraft Rectangle Salad Box, 17 x 11 cm with Window - 250 pcs
Short Description: Hotpack - Kraft Rectangle Salad Box, 17 x 11 cm with Window - 250 pcs
Description:
Hotpack - Kraft Rectangle Salad Box, 17 x 11 cm with Window - 250 pcs - Whether you are packaging and selling salads, appetites, one piece cakes, pies, cookies, cupcakes, or your signature muffins, this box is sure to do the trick! Its auto-popup design saves time and makes assembly quick so that you can offer fast and efficient service at your bakery. At the same time, the viewing window displays the product for quick and easy identification. Made of durable kraft paperboard, this box is built strong to ensure your items are protected while on display or in transport. 
The natural kraft construction means it's an eco-friendly alternative to traditional white or printed boxes, yet it's just as strong as those comparable options. With this natural kraft box, you'll be able to increase impulse sales of your most popular food items, while reinforcing your commitment to the environment. It is even unmarked, so you can quickly add custom labels and stamps for a pop of personalization.

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - 12/16 Oz Paper Hot Cup Sleeve - 1000 pcs
Short Description: Hotpack - 12/16 Oz Paper Hot Cup Sleeve - 1000 pcs
Description:
Hotpack - 12/16 Oz Paper Hot Cup Sleeve - 1000 pcs - Eliminate the need to double cup your hot beverages with this Choice coffee cup sleeve! A great addition to coffee shops, self-serve buffet lines, cafeterias, and office break rooms, this coffee sleeve provides a simple, practical solution to holding hot beverages. This sleeve easily slides over cups to provide an insulated layer of protection between hands and the hot surface. Designed to fit 12, 16 oz hot paper cups, this sleeve's compatibility with multiple cup sizes reduces product inventory. Simply stack coffee cup sleeves up next to your cups and lids at your break station, or place them in a compatible coffee cup sleeve dispenser for organized storage. Add a personal touch to each beverage served as you write your customer's name on this sleeve. The plain Kraft paperboard is perfect for keeping track of orders during busy service.

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - Paper Straw Aqua Blue, 6 mm - 5000 pcs
Short Description: Hotpack - Paper Straw Aqua Blue, 6 mm - 5000 pcs
Description:
Hotpack - Paper Straw Aqua Blue, 6 mm - 5000 pcs - We make our environmentally responsible choices by serving beverages with very own Hotpack's assorted strip unwrapped paper straw! Made of a special paper, this straw is a great alternative to plastic straws that remain in the environment for hundreds of years. Whether used at a restaurant, cafe, or concession stand, your patrons will be sure to appreciate your environmental consciousness and effort to reduce our carbon footprint. This straw is also versatile and can be used for both hot beverages as well as cold. Each straw also features an attractive spiraled design that is perfect for everything from a specialty beverage.
Features and Usage 
1. Unwrapped for convenient, easy access
2. Can be used for both hot and cold beverages
3. Environmentally conscious option for restaurants, cafes, and concessions
4. Colors include: Classic Red, Aqua Blue, Dark Blue, Candy Purple, Black Beauty, and Plain White
5. Disposable for easy cleanup
6. Perfect for food trucks, fairs, or diners
7. Designed for quality, single-service use

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - 12 Oz Kraft Paper Noodle Bowl with Lid - 250 pcs
Short Description: Hotpack - 12 Oz Kraft Paper Noodle Bowl with Lid - 250 pcs
Description:
Hotpack - 12 Oz Kraft Paper Noodle Bowl with Lid - 250 pcs - Serve your takeout and delivery orders with nature-friendly style in our 12 Ounce Kraft Noodle Take Out Bowl. Constructed from nature-friendly Kraft paper, these small Chinese take-out boxes are 100% recyclable for quick and easy cleanup. Their grease-resistant interior lining is perfectly suited for serving messier foods like sticky honey garlic chicken or saucy lo mien noodles, and their tight lid design is built to prevent spills and messes while in transport. These catering food containers are great for serving small portions of appetizers, salads, side dishes, and more. Their natural Kraft brown finish adds a professional touch to the look of your takeout orders, and their classic shape enables easy stacking so that your staff can quickly wrap up orders. 

Product Specification
Ideal for to-go soups, stews, pasta, and steamed veggies
The versatile size makes it great for multiple servings and won't leak
The sleek exterior allows you to write orders and customer names directly on the cup
Made for durability and moisture resistance
Tightly-rolled rim guarantees a secure fit with compatible lids (Sold Separately)

Hotpack - 32 Oz Kraft Paper Noodle Bowl with Lid - 250 pcs - Serve your takeout and delivery orders with nature-friendly style in our 12 Ounce Kraft Noodle Take Out Bowl. Constructed from nature-friendly Kraft paper, these small Chinese take-out boxes are 100% recyclable for quick and easy cleanup. Their grease-resistant interior lining is perfectly suited for serving messier foods like sticky honey garlic chicken or saucy lo mien noodles, and their tight lid design is built to prevent spills and messes while in transport. These catering food containers are great for serving small portions of appetizers, salads, side dishes, and more. Their natural Kraft brown finish adds a professional touch to the look of your takeout orders, and their classic shape enables easy stacking so that your staff can quickly wrap up orders. 

Product Specification
Ideal for to-go soups, stews, pasta, and steamed veggies
The versatile size makes it great for multiple servings and won't leak
The sleek exterior allows you to write orders and customer names directly on the cup
Made for durability and moisture resistance
Tightly-rolled rim guarantees a secure fit with compatible lids (Sold Separately)

Description:
Hotpack - Round Paper Pail Box, 16 Oz - 500 pcs - This 16 oz round paper pail box take out container's white exterior makes it a popular addition to trendy restaurants and cafes, wedding receptions, and Chinese / Asian eateries. Use it for just about any of your menu items. The leak-and grease-resistant packaging keeps hot, cold, wet, or dry foods fresh from kitchen to destination. Plus, the efficient one-piece design of the package maintains freshness by retaining heat and venting steam. This take out container's versatile size makes it perfect for serving sides of fried rice, white rice, or lo mein. The container is designed with a convenient microwaveable design that's moderate heat lamp tolerant, too.

Leak-and grease-resistant packaging keeps hot, cold, wet, or dry foods safe during transport

One piece design provides easy assembly and no lid confusion

Name/Product Title: Hotpack - Paper Soup Bowl with Lid 250 Ml - 1000 pcs
